title: Game developer distribution worldwide 2014 - 2017 , by gender
summary: You are viewing a chart of multi-line type with 3 lines denoting Men, Women, and Transgender/Androgynous/Other. The y axis indicates the Share of respondents and the x axis indicates Year.
Overall Men, Women, and Transgender/Androgynous/Other are roughly constant,  throughout the Year
The ranking of the lines from topmost to botommmost is as follows: 1. Men, 2. Women, and lastly, 3. Transgender/Androgynous/Other.
Overall across the Year, Men mostly maintained the highest Share of respondents when compared to others with a mean value of 74.25, and it peaked at 2014.
Followed by Women which ranks as the second topmpost line , with an average of 22.0 Share of respondents,reaching its highest point  at 2016 with a value of 23.0.
Transgender/Androgynous/Other mostly had the least Share of respondents with a mean value of 3.68, which peaked at 2017 with a value of 5.0.
